Titolo: Mighty Atom (1988 video game)

Anno: 1988

Descrizione: Mighty Atom (鉄腕アトム, Tetsuwan Atomu) is a side-scrolling platform game published by Konami based on the manga and anime franchise Mighty Atom (Astro Boy in English) by Osamu Tezuka. The game was released exclusively in Japan for the Famicom on February 26, 1988.